&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Once this is done for all pages, hugo-coder will render the &lt;a href=&#34;#conclusion&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;See also in &amp;hellip;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; section at the article footer.&lt;/p&gt;
